    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and presents in showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or imperfections, recently treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating for lasting protection. The interior is equally breathtaking; the high-grade leather remains taut and supple without a single bolster crease or sign of wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every button, switch, and digital display operates with factory precision, and the cabin still retains its original new-car aroma. Mechanically, the vehicle is indistinguishable from new, boasting a comprehensive service history exclusively performed by certified technicians. The engine bay is spotless, the undercarriage is free of any road debris or corrosion, and the tires are a fresh set of premium pilots. This is a single-owner vehicle with a clean title, two master keys, and a complete set of original manuals. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
